*'''2005''': An ordinary man doesn’t jump the Snake River Canyon / with nothing underneath his ass / but a two-wheeled, fin-stabilised X-1 Skycycle / and a seven-figure guarantee from some '''macher''' in LA. &mdash; August Kleinzahler , in 'A Valentine’s: Regarding the Impractibility of Our Love', ''London Review of Books'', Vol. 27 No.20, 20 October 2005, page 6.